    "description": "<strong>Bill is going through a tough time in his life, he lost meaning and purpose. <br>But one night, a UFO crashes in front of his little home in the woods. <br>The passenger is an unconscious baby alien.<br>You are his only chance of survival!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features :</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Collect Resources</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/2065f3faa42d076bfc63c2fc609715e3.poster.avif?t=1700736296\" width=592 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/2065f3faa42d076bfc63c2fc609715e3.webm?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/2065f3faa42d076bfc63c2fc609715e3.mp4?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Plant and grow your own vegetables.<br>Grow anything you like to cook with an increasing tech system to make farming easier and easier.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><u>Interact with everything</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/f9bcefc5737fbb15dbd1f44e43989836.poster.avif?t=1700736296\" width=516 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/f9bcefc5737fbb15dbd1f44e43989836.webm?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/f9bcefc5737fbb15dbd1f44e43989836.mp4?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Everything is interactable in the game, lamps, radio, tv, and many other machines<br></li><li><u>Crafting</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/38a848426fc0946dafc67e2570ac2377.poster.avif?t=1700736296\" width=502 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/38a848426fc0946dafc67e2570ac2377.webm?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/38a848426fc0946dafc67e2570ac2377.mp4?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Everything you need in the game is craftable.<br>Collect items in the forest and craft from specialized crafting tables: Woodcraft, Kitchen, Electronic, Forge, Chemistry<br></li><li><u>Building</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/5f89bccf0322885aad25d5246933e184.poster.avif?t=1700736296\" width=744 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/5f89bccf0322885aad25d5246933e184.webm?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1897470/extras/5f89bccf0322885aad25d5246933e184.mp4?t=1700736296\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Create new rooms or utilities and place them where you want.<br>Make your house unique and as big as you like.<br></li><li><u>Buy and sell items</u><br>Buy online broken devices, restore them with new parts, and sell them for a better price.<br></li><li><u>Restoring</u><br>Take any broken item and give it a new life using your master skills.<br></li><li><u>Take care of the baby alien and yourself</u><br>Sleep, eat well and entertain yourself, it's not only about work.<br></li><li><u>Decorate your home</u><br>Use plants, lamps, paintings, and posters to decorate your home and make it as cozy as you like.</li></ul></li></ul>",
